text: Kathryn (Katie) Nageotte (born June 13, 1991) is an American athlete, specializing in pole vaulting. ==National & international events== {| |- !colspan=7| Representing United States of America |- |rowspan=3|2018 || 2018 NACAC Championships || Toronto, Canada || bgcolor=gold|1st || Pole Vault || CR |- || Athletics World Cup || London, United Kingdom || bgcolor=silver|2nd || Pole Vault || |- ||2018 IAAF World Indoor Championships || Birmingham, United Kingdom || 5th || Pole Vault || |- | 2015 || 2015 NACAC Championships || San José ||align = "center "bgcolor = cc9966 |3rd ||Pole Vault || |} Katie Nageotte was signed from Adidas in 2016-2018. Katie Nageotte signed with Nike in 2018.
